By sharing a picture and tagging a friend, each person can help delivering 1 million meals. Thus, 1 digital t-shirt = usd 12.50 = 50 meals. Michael kors aims to donate up to 1,000,000 meals. username: I asked one of my favourite image makers, Leo Berne @leo_berne, to share a photo this week. Leo is one fourth of Megaforce, the team that made Rihanna's BBHMM video, Brodinski's Can't Help Myself (one of my favourites last year) and roughly a million other amazing videos. He chose this image by French photographer Axel Morin @axelmorin75.
Leo says, "He is a talented and prolific street photographer. He did a great series in France with people on motorbikes.
I really like how he plays with contrasts and colors, he's got that particular analog feeling that I love.
I don't know if he sometimes shoots digital but if he does, I surely want to know how he manages to end up with this look!"
